This creamy chicken & mushroom pasta is a go-to comfort meal — and it gets a flavor boost from @pompeian Extra Virgin Olive Oil. I used the Smooth variety for sautéing, but you can pick your favorite from their line: Robust, Fresh & Fruity, or Smooth. Here’s how to make it:

⸻

Simple Creamy Chicken & Mushroom Pasta

Ingredients:
	•	2 cups shell pasta
	•	1 cup chopped chicken
	•	1 cup sliced mushrooms
	•	2 cloves garlic, minced
	•	1 cup heavy cream
	•	2 tbsp @pompeian Extra Virgin Olive Oil
	•	Salt & pepper to taste

Instructions:
	1.	Cook pasta and set aside.
	2.	In a pan, heat olive oil and sauté garlic.
	3.	Add chicken and cook through.
	4.	Add mushrooms and cook until soft.
	5.	Pour in cream, let it simmer.
	6.	Mix in pasta, season with salt & pepper.

⸻

✨ So simple, so good — and made better with Pompeian Olive Oil. #PompeianPartner #TasteThePompeianDifference #EasyDinners #OliveOilLove #PompeianPartner #PompeianEVOO #gifted, #pompeian, #pompeianpartner #ad
